otherNames: ひろがるスカイ！プリキュア
synopsis:
A major incident has occurred in the peaceful Sky Land!?
The young Princess Elle has been kidnapped by the monsters of Underg Empire!
A brave young girl, Sora, follows the princess through a mysterious hole.
"TV"? "Cars"? Are those some kind of magic tools!?!?
But there's no time to be surprised! She has to get the princess back to the castle...!
Flying between two worlds! The adventure with the Pretty Cure begins now!

It's hero time!
